{"type":null,"faqId":46161,"title":"摄像头需要手动翻转，不是电动的？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>7i翻转镜头设计的两大挑战：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、翻转组件的可靠性，7i翻转组件采用全金属结构MIMI工艺，每一台均可支持10万次翻转；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、7i采用内嵌式翻转设计，一改以往因翻转需要新增大量组件（比如保护壳，转轴等）而带来的手机整体厚、笨、大的现象；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>这是一种全新技术，而采用机械设计风格所带来的机械质感与手感也是7i独具的。。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1941","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376113000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":60,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"摄像头","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}